Property.Name: QueryScript
Property.Value: SELECT DISTINCT Logement.* FROM [Logement] AS Logement JOIN [Avis] AS Avis ON Logement.[idLogement] = Avis.[idLogement] WHERE (SELECT AVG([note]) FROM Avis WHERE Avis.idLogement = Logement.IdLogement)>(SELECT AVG([note]) FROM [Avis])

Property.Name: HeaderContents
BodyScript
Property.Value: SELECT * FROM [Logement] WHERE [DateCreation] BETWEEN CONVERT(DATETIME,DATEDIFF(DAY,30,GETDATE())) AND GETDATE()

Property.Name: QueryScript
Property.Value:
SELECT [IdReservationLogement], [DateDebut], [DateFin], Logement.[adressePays]
FROM [ReservationLogement] AS reservation JOIN [Logement] AS Logement ON reservation.[IdLogement]=Logement.[IdLogement]
